moment to compose himself. You wait, unsure what to do.
   'Are you certain?' he askes as he tries to rebuild his composure. 'There's
no doubt? Those monsters turned him into a... into a mop?'
   You nod, hardly sure what to say.
   The man's eyes redden and begin to well up with tears. He slides a small
purse of money across to you, and turns away.
~
