   'Yes, you,' she says as you squeeze between chairs in the tightly-packed
cafe to get to her. 'Oh, you have amassed quite the collection. You must've
plumbed the tower for its deepest secrets to find all this. Puts you in rare
company, indeed. Did you eat the mushroom? Henri ate the mushroom the first
